Translated_Text: IMO, this presidential debate, sir, is superior in mastering the material and data. Sir, he is superior in the debate strategy that successfully made his opponent, especially Prabowo, break down from the beginning. He was busy controlling his emotions. Sir, he tended to be defensive, even to refute the wrong attacks on him, he did not fight back with arguments based on existing rules. For example, the attack that Mr. Anies meant touched on our cyberspace which is not safe so that the Ministry of Defense had its cyber security breached. This is an ironic note for the Ministry of Defense, even though the duties, functions and authorities related to cyber security are not the realm of the Ministry of Defense but by the BSSN which is under the auspices of the Coordinating Ministry for Political, Legal and Security Affairs and its coordination is directly with the President. Anies highlighted the inequality where the welfare of TNI soldiers from salaries and housing allowances, according to him, was not given enough attention, while Prabowo as the Ministry of Defense has tens of thousands of hectares of land. The responsibility for the welfare of soldiers is the realm of the TNI Commander as the party proposing the increase. The TNI Commander coordinated with the Ministry of Finance and the Ministry of Defense brought it to the DPRRI meeting and then approved by the President. Mr. Ganjar is very good at the material, arguments and choices given by Ganjar are also usually not as spicy as Mr. Anies, but The questions that Ganjar asked were indeed urgent, for example when he questioned Prabowo about why MEF III had only just been achieved from the minimum target, Ganjar knew that this was urgent because now it had entered, which means it was the last year for the Ministry of Defense to achieve its target in MEF III, plus the Minister of Defense must have a defense plan for next year to be continued by whoever holds the position of the next Minister of Defense, Re Mazzinigsp.

Translated_Text: After going through a long, steep and winding journey, Ganjar Pranowo's group finally arrived at a hamlet called Gunungsari Karanggayam Village, Kebumen Regency. It was raining lightly, but it did not dampen the enthusiasm of the residents who welcomed them. There were no signs of fatigue on Ganjar's face. He immediately went around the village and greeted the residents. Ganjar's footsteps landed at the house of the Gunungsari village head named Sukarjo while lying down and sipping coffee. Ganjar listened to the complaints of his residents one by one, some of whom told stories of individual problems to collective problems such as the potential for village tourism. Text: oleh septian  dengan nada meletupletup tangan memukulmukul udara prabowo subianto meluapkan kekesalannya karena bisnisbisnisnya mandek setelah dirinya tidak berkuasa momen di mata najwa itu jelas mengakhiri rasa penasaran publik kenapa dia betulbetul sangat bernafsu menggenggam kekuasaan ya ada dendam yang belum dituntaskannya di masa kekuasaan orde baru prabowo memang bagai anak emas karena mampu membangun banyak bisnis untuk mempertebal kekayaannya sampaisampai ratusan ribu hektar lahan negara dia kuasai namun setelah orde baru tumbang nepotisme perlahanlahan mulai disikat dan ini berdampak terhadap prabowo satusatunya agar bisa mengembalikan semua kejayaan itu adalah dengan meraih kekuasaan sudah pasti sesuatu yang diraih dengan ambisi menggebugebu akan dimanfaatkan betul jika sudah dalam genggaman begitupun kekuasaan bagi prabowo ia akan menggunakannya untuk memenuhi hasrat pribadi dan kelompoknya lain tidak kita bisa berkaca dari proyek food estate di kalteng baru menjabat menteri saja proyek triliunan itu menguap entah kemana ada hektar lahan singkong mangkrak dan sawah baru tak kunjung panen proyek itu dijalankan pt agrinas milik kementerian pertahanan orangorang kepercyaan prabowo di gerindra banyak menjabat pimpinan disana jajaran komisaris juga diisi para purnawirawan tni yang juga anggota tim kampanye prabowo pada cerita mungkin akan berbeda jika proyek pangan itu dipegang oleh ahlinya tentu saja dari perencanaan dan pelaksanaan akan lebih matang dan terukur kalau sudah pengedepankan nepotisme begini wajar publik curiga proyek itu hanya lahan untuk mengeruk duit rakyat itu baru food estate bayangkan jika prabowo berkuasa ada banyak sektor lain yang akan dikuasai dia dan kronikroninya sebut saja misalnya program makan siang dan bagibagi susu yang anggarannya mencapai rp triliun pertahun untuk susu perah saja produksi dalam negeri kita hanya sanggup memenuhi persen penduduk sisanya impor dari austalia dan selandia baru sudah pasti jika program tak masuk akal itu dipaksakan justru akan semakin menambah beban impor bisa ditebak yang diuntungkan selain peternak asing adalah importir yang sudah pasti akan diisi kronikroni prabowo disitu akan sangat rawan permainan dan celah korupsi karena beban anggaran itu sektorsektor belanja negara yang lain pun akan terdampak pantas saja prabowo sendiri di acara sarasehan ekonom menyebut anggaran program ini akan diambil dari dana pendidikan dan bansos artinya dana bos ataupun subsidi pendidikan akan dipangkas dan bantuan sosial yang selama ini dinikmati warga kurang mampu juga akan dipotong belum lagi wacana menaikkan pajak yang jelas akan membenani rakyat jika dipikirpikir situasinya betulbetul akan semakin kacau tatanan dan juga program yang selama ini dirasakan manfaatnya untuk rakyat akan dirusak hanya untuk program makan siang gratis yang sebenarnya cuma menguntungkan kronikroni prabowo re melihatindo

Translated_Text: by septian with a bursting tone of hands hitting the air prabowo subianto vented his frustration because his businesses had stalled after he was no longer in power the moment in najwa's eyes clearly ended the public's curiosity as to why he was really so eager to grasp power yes there was a grudge that had not been resolved during the new order era prabowo was indeed like a golden child because he was able to build many businesses to thicken his wealth to the point that he controlled hundreds of thousands of hectares of state land but after the new order fell nepotism slowly began to be swept away and this had an impact on prabowo the only way to restore all that glory was to gain power it was certain that something that was achieved with great ambition would be utilized properly if it was already in his grasp likewise power for prabowo he would use it to fulfill his personal and group desires otherwise we can't look at the food estate project in central kalimantan when he had just become a minister the trillion project evaporated who knows where there were hectares of cassava land that was stalled and new rice fields that had not yet been harvested the project was run by pt agrinas owned by the ministry of defense people's trust in prabowo in Gerindra has many leadership positions there, the board of commissioners is also filled with retired TNI who are also members of Prabowo's campaign team. The story might be different if the food project was handled by experts. Of course, the planning and implementation would be more mature and measurable. If nepotism is prioritized like this, it is natural for the public to suspect that the project is just a place to take people's money. That's the food estate. Imagine if Prabowo were in power, there would be many other sectors that he and his cronies would control. For example, the lunch program and milk distribution with a budget of up to IDR trillion per year. For dairy milk alone, our domestic production is only able to meet 100% of the population. The rest is imported from Australia and New Zealand. It is certain that if this unreasonable program is forced, it will actually increase the import burden. It can be guessed that those who benefit apart from foreign farmers are importers who will definitely be filled with Prabowo's cronies. There will be a lot of corruption and corruption because of the budget burden. Other state spending sectors will also be affected. It is only natural that Prabowo himself at the economist's discussion event said that the budget for this program would be taken from education funds and social assistance, meaning BOS funds or Education subsidies will be cut and social assistance that has been enjoyed by the poor will also be cut, not to mention the discourse on increasing taxes which will clearly burden the people. If you think about it, the situation will really become more chaotic and the programs that have been felt to be beneficial for the people will be destroyed just for the free lunch program which actually only benefits Prabowo's cronies.

Translated_Text: abah anies promises to revise the kpk law to restore public trust presidential candidate presidential candidate number anies baswedan promises to improve the corruption eradication commission kpk if he wins the presidential election the first step anies takes to improve the anti-corruption agency is to revise the law law number 2015 concerning amendments to the law number 2015 concerning the corruption eradication commission according to anies the step to revise the law aims to restore public trust as well as return the kpk to its former state as an institution that has the ability to eradicate corruption we are returning the kpk to its legal authority again as it was before and this means revising the kpk law we want this revision to be able to return the kpk to a strong position said anies in his presentation at the integrity nail event for presidential and vice presidential candidates at the kpk building in Jakarta on Wednesday night in addition to improving the law anies is also committed to creating high ethical standards within the kpk anies wants all elements of the kpk to return to their former state when its employees did not want to eat or participate in activities that were not funded by the kpk those high standards must be returned to the KPK so that not only does the law provide strength and independence but also in it both leaders and staff work with a very high code of ethics, said Anies, Anies also wants to improve recruitment both at the leadership level and at the employee level as previously conveyed by the president, the leadership level and staff recruitment which are not only looking for work but also become a place to eradicate corruption, he added, source re tijabar

Text: cara anies entaskan miskin ekstrem penyumbang terbesar kemiskinan adalah masyarakat yang berada di desa desa pesisir bagaimana cara anies baswedan entaskan kemiskinan ekstrem berdasarkan pengalaman gubernur dki jakarta penulis rusdianto samawa fourbes indonesia calon presiden anies baswedan yang diusung oleh koalisi perubahan membawa visi misi indonesia yang mengandung unsur unsur penting yang penting agar menjadi catatan rakyat indonesia visi misi tersebut komitmen entaskan seluruh masalah yang dianggap emergency atas kegagalan rezim saat ini visi misi indonesia pasangan amin mulai dari kinerja pertumbuhan ekonomi atau produk domestik bruto pdb per kapita pengangguran hingga penuntasan kemiskinan ekstrem visi misi tersebut lebih ditekankan kepada kemakmuran yang dirasakan seluruh penduduk tanah air oleh karena itu ketimpangan harus menjadi fokus yang selama ini rezim gagal total tuntaskan ketimpangan sangat nyata yang kita hadapi dan menjadi pr sesungguhnya pasangan amin anies baswedan muhaimin iskandar juga menilai pertumbuhan ekonomi indonesia belum berhasil menyelesaikan masalah pengangguran seperti diketahui ekonomi indonesia tumbuh di kisaran selama kuartal beruntun namun jumlah pengangguran masih cukup tinggi adapun bps mencatat jumlah pengangguran di indonesia mencapai juta orang pada februari berkurang sekitar ribu orang dibanding februari ditengah merosotnya kepercayaan rakyat terhadap pemerintah dan negara polemik pengangguran dan kemiskinan ekstrem belum juga usai dibahas hal ini sangat bahayakan kedaulatan negara pemerintah berbohong kepada rakyat yang munculkan indeks kemiskinan ekstrem yang diklaim tinggal atau sekitar juta penduduk jumlah tersebut mayoritas masyarakat pesisir upaya pengentasan kemiskinan di pesisir itu langkah mendasar untuk menetapkan indonesia masuk kategori midle income trap pemerintah umumkan keberhasilannya dari menurunkan kemiskinan ekstrem padahal kebohongan besar diketahui angka kemiskinan saat ini sebesar cara anies entaskan miskin ekstrem calon presiden koalisi perubahan anies baswedan menjanjikan kemiskinan di indonesia bisa turun ke pada mendatang diketahui angka kemiskinan saat ini sebesar harapannya kemiskinan ekstremnya bisa kata anies dalam acara sarasehan ekonom indonesia di menara bank mega jakarta rabu sala satu paling rumit dipahami yakni kebijakan pemerintah tidak berperan lakukan intervensi income dalam mendorong distribusi hasil pertanian peternakan dan kelautan perikanan faktor kegagalan kebijakan rezim saat ini sangat nyata pengalaman anies baswedan saat gubernur dki jakarta bahwa september persentase penduduk miskin di jakarta mencapai persen saat ini tingkat kemiskinan turun hingga persen angka itu terkecil di indonesia sementara jawa tengah paling tinggi angka kemiskinan dibanding daerah lain di indonesia tentu cara anies menurunkan angka kemiskinan itu melalui kebijakan transparansi harga dipasar lokal sehingga ada mekanisme kompetisi yang berjalan dan bisa untungkan konsumen harga diklaim bisa turun tanpa harus ada intervensi dari pemerintah salah satu hal konkret yang akan dilakukan anies adalah dengan memastikan biaya hidup terjangkau salah satunya melalui komponen harga pangan kepastian suplai pangan dengan harga yang murah menargetkan pertumbuhan ekonomi ratarata mencapai melalui strategi untuk keluar dari middle income trap secara inklusif dengan meningkatkan peran koperasi dan umkm dukungan usaha baru di seluruh wilayah indonesia pemanfaatan infrastruktur ekonomi digital pengelolaan ekonomi hijaubiru serta pertumbuhan industri manufaktur di sumber cara anies entaskan miskin ekstrem

Translated_Text: fear mongering yes you did not misread this article is an attempt to frame prabowo and gibran this article is my opinion about the conditions that will occur if they are both elected as president and vice president of the republic of indonesia this article was made to make you think twice about choosing them both this article is a negative campaign as a counter argument for all the gimmicks of joy and happiness and moving on reflecting on the experience of the presidential and vice presidential debates regardless of what prabowo and gibran convey regardless of the arguments and counter arguments that they both convey I see a tendency for uncontrolled emotional outburst the old man seems to point at the interlocutor the young man seems provocative by becoming a cheerleader in both debates and this is the face of the person who might become the highest leader of the republic of indonesia if you don't immediately think again then what makes us have to think again netizens hasn't the presidential power been reduced and balanced since the amendment with the strengthening of legislative and judicial powers don't forget the amount of salary of members of the dpr and the salary of judges is determined through government regulations don't forget the amount of allowances for members of the dpr and judges is determined by presidential decree don't forget most members of the dpr are people who are not finished with their lives are still looking for income, income that if honest and not looking for projects is determined by the government cq the president and vice president if the president is prevented from doing so with a bargaining position like that, can the legislature and judiciary be fair in assessing and/or supervising the government's actions? This could be worse if the coalition supporting the president dominates the legislature, the general chairman of the party becomes president, the general chairman of the party becomes a minister, just forget about the check and balance function of the legislature, just assume that the government's authority with the approval of the DPR which is regulated in the UUD is the same as the government's authority because the DPR will definitely agree that the absence of the check and balance function of the legislature, coupled with the tendency for uncontrolled emotional outbursts from the president who, if prevented from doing so, will still be replaced by the vice president, should make us think twice about voting for Prabowo and Gibran in the presidential election in any year, think again before choosing Prabowo, he has past debts that have not been resolved as one of the general chairmen of the dominant party in the DPR, he can propose to form a human rights court to examine and decide all the annual gossip that sticks to him, think again before choosing Gibran, he is not the best young person that Indonesia has, he is on the ballot paper because he is the son of the president, the son of the president who is said to have achieved not young people who have achieved and happen to be the president's children, think again before choosing them both, they are a couple who enjoy decisions taken in conditions where there are ethical violations, the formula can be concluded as follows, if they are both elected, Indonesia will be led by a pair of people with a tendency towards uncontrolled emotional outbursts, enjoyers of no ethics, the absence of legislative and judicial checks and balances, imagine the formula above before you make your choice, imagine the formula above when you start to be lulled by moving on, gemoy, downstreaming, etc., re, traders, critics

Translated_Text: PrabowoJokowi's Manunggaling My brother, recently a video has been circulating of Mr. Prabowo's statement that he has now united with Mr. Jokowi. This statement is not strange because Mr. Prabowo has chosen President Jokowi's biological son, Gibran Rakabuming Raka, as his vice presidential candidate to accompany him in this presidential election contest. Thus, the process of uniting Mr. Prabowo and Mr. Jokowi has been almost complete. The question is, who benefits and who is harmed in this PrabowoJokowi Manunggaling process? In our view, the union of the two elements of fire and water in the presidential election and that in this presidential election actually does not benefit anyone, in fact it tends to harm President Jokowi. You can see how President Jokowi has degraded himself in order to pass Prabowo's desire to unite with him. The scandal of Gibran's passing as Prabowo's vice presidential candidate in the Constitutional Court has truly resulted in the stigma of an illegitimate child. The constitution has really resulted in the stigma of President Jokowi's biological child. The neutrality of the president as head of state in overseeing the election process is now also really in doubt. There is even an assumption that the president is no longer truly acting as the head of state who protects all in this democratic party but has become the head of the campaign team of one of the candidates who are contesting the state palace and is even suspected of being the winning post for one of the candidates, the mobilization of large-scale social assistance, the deployment of state apparatus and the president's partisan comments certainly strengthen the indication that the president is increasingly degrading himself and his good achievements for almost ten years, even though he has sided with his old enemy, are like lifting a submerged tree in a Malay proverb, with the assumption that Prabowo will unite with Jokowi who still has a high approval rating, this presidential election should have been over in one round, but in fact Prabowo's electability is still stagnant at below percent and tends to decrease due to blunders and personal limitations and the character of Mr. Prabowo who is unable to appear classy in his campaign to the wider public, in the end we only witness President Jokowi who is full of achievements increasingly insulting and degrading himself at the end of his power, we do not yet know what the end of President Jokowi's power will be like, who is now uniting with the fire element, which is certain now We are witnessing various unethical maneuvers that have the potential to endanger democracy and damage the integrity of the nation and state. We only pray that the election will be fair, honest and peaceful and that the winner is truly a figure who unites the kawulo gusti, not the uniting of the elements of water and fire.
